	name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
	stars INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	image VARCHAR(255), 
	element VARCHAR(50), 
	archetype VARCHAR(50), 
	nb_skill_ups INTEGER, 
	leader_skill_id INTEGER, 
	hp INTEGER, 
	attack INTEGER, 
	defense INTEGER, 
	speed INTEGER, 
	crit_rate INTEGER, 
	crit_dmg INTEGER, 
	resistance INTEGER, 
	accuracy INTEGER, 
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(leader_skill_id) REFERENCES leader_skills (id)
);
